OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry in the east with
OL,6,Fsunny spells and variable cloud.
OL,7,FCloudy in the west with a few light
OL,8,Fshowers in the morning. Some more
OL,9,Fpersistent rain spreads east in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with some
OL,13,Flight rain in the west, staying dry in
OL,14,Fthe east. Remaining cloudy in the west
OL,15,Fovernight but generally drier. Dry
OL,16,Fwith clear spells in east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
