OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome bright spells in the
OL,6,Fnorth and east at first. Otherwise
OL,7,Fcloudy with increasingly persistent
OL,8,Frain in the west, turning heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes. Rain light and patchy in the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,13,Fchangeable, often cloudy and windy few
OL,14,Fdays with spells of rain, occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy and persistent in the west. Best
OL,16,Fof the drier, brighter spells around
OL,17,Fthe Moray Firth.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
